| 
| A routine parameter variable (read-only).
| 

class BMM_PARAMETER
    is_a BMM_READONLY_VARIABLE

feature_group ("access")

    | 
    | Optional read/write direction of the parameter. If none-supplied, the parameter is treated
    | as `in`, i.e. readable.
    | 
    prop direction: BMM_PARAMETER_DIRECTION;


end
